{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75cb03d85d","title":"给许德等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cb7165bb4f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":2,"articleId":"75cb03d85d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a5dcc6a858","type":"paragraph","text":"给许德等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"51204b69e3","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年11月2日）各位教授先生们","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"18da63f2df","type":"paragraph","text":"收到惠赠各物（火腿、时表等），夷心感谢，不胜荣幸！我们与你们之间，精神上完全是一致的。我们的故人只有一个，就是日本帝国主义，我们正准备一切迅速地进到团结全国出兵抗日，我们与你们见面之期已不远了。为驱逐日本帝国主义而奋斗，为中华民主共和国而奋斗，这是全国人民的旗帜，也就是我们与你们共同的旗帜！谨致民族革命的敬礼！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"671d811031","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"fb6f223945","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二号","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"7520fe99a0","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]许德（1890—1990），江西九江人。早年参加辛玄革命和五四运动。1936年任北京大学教授，与马叙伦、杨秀峰、张申府、程希孟等教授组织“北平文化界救国会”，积极从事抗日救亡运动。新中国成立后，任第四、第五届政协全国委员会副主席，第四至第六届全国人大常委会副委员长，九三学社中央主席。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"693dae23ab","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]1935年底，许德和夫人劳君展得悉毛泽东已到达陕北，买了30多双布鞋、12块怀表和十几只火腿，委托中共地下党的徐冰、张晓梅设法转送到陕北。医旅多该加！旅，道","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"cb8e712ad4","type":"paragraph","text":"人民M放生物见我们与伤和中梦医1和阁斗渝肥医李阁万科应斗九我们与物们机色毛州多子","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"e51898991c","type":"paragraph","text":"冠空阁3新新储上常全是致个们粘人布干谢生事街间精神","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"3e00f7d4a6","type":"paragraph","text":"无位粘生全门！一国腔加监测筑有国上发九点","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"a6e58d2695","type":"paragraph","text":"利意（大特表等）烹如心中A吉宾","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"},{"id":"0006e24d44","type":"paragraph","text":"6毛泽东致许德等信的手稿","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d"}],"page":{"id":"e71fc7bcf2","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"75cb03d85d","start":272,"end":273}}}},"__N_SSG":true}